      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Dehlu/ eekſch tahm Deenahm U-\njus/Jotama/ Akafa/ Ifrijuſ/\no Kehnizu no Juha/ un eekſch\ntahm Deenahm Jerobeama/ ta\nDehla Joata/ ta Kehnizu no\nIsraëka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schis irr tas Eefahkumâ\nta KUNGA Wahrdâ zaur Ose-\nn. Tas KUNG S fazzija uſ\nOfeju: Eij/ neimmees weenn\nManko-Geewu/ un Mankas-\nBehrnuſ/ jo ta Semme dsen-\nnahs no ta KUNGA tai Man-\nibai pakkat.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nogahje wiſch/ un\nkehme Gomeri weenu Meitu no\nDiblaim/ un winna tappe gruh-\nta/ un dseindeja winnam weenn\nDehlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNG S fazzija\nuhs winnu: Sanz winna Wahrd-\nDu Jesreëts: Jo pahr ihfo Laiku\noeemeklechn es Jesreëta Affins-\nWainas/pahr to Namnu Jeus/\nan pabetſchu to Walstibu ta I-\nraëta Namma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tai Deena Salaustichn es\nIsraëta Stohpu eekſch Jesreëta\nEeleijas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winna tappe atkat\nruhta/ un dseindeja weenn Mei-\ny. Un Wiſch fazzija uhs to:\nNosauz winnas Wahrdâ LoRi-\nmo/ jo es joprohjam wairs ne\napschehloſchohs pahr to Israëta\nNamnu/ bet es gribbu tohs tee-\nchain aiswest.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet pahr to Namnu Juha apschehloſchohs es/ un atpe-\ntſchu tohs zaur to KUNG U\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "winno Deewu/ un es ne gribbu\ntohs atpeſtiht zaur Stohpu/neds\nzaur Sobbinu/ neds zaur Kar-\nen/ neds zaur Sirgeem/ neds\nJahtneekem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad ta nu to LoRiamo bij\natschkihrufi/ tad tappe winna\ngruhta/ un dseindeja weenn\nDehlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Wiſch fazzija: No-\nsauz winna Wahrdâ Lo-Ammi/\njo juhs ne effat manni Laudis/\ntad neds es juhsfu buhfcbu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta II. Nodalla.\nPapreekschsluddinasfhana no to Pagaknu Alijs-\nnaschanas ta jauna Testamento Laikâ: 10.\nAr weenu gauschu Suhdfschanu pahr to\nLauschu garrigu Mauzibu: 2. Un ar pees-\nliktu Eepreezinaschannu/ ka Deews tomehr ar\njawu Draudsibu eekſch Muhschibas fader-\nrejees: 18.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Omeir tas Puks to\nIsraëta Behrnu buhs\nta Juhras Siniltis/ kas ne warr mehrohts/ neds skai-\ntihts tapt. Un tas notiks tai\nWeetâ/ kur uhs teem buhs faz-\nzihts: Inhs ne effat manni Lau-\ndis/ tops us teem fazzihts: Juhs\nBehrni ta dshwa Deewa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee Behrni Juha/ un tee Israëta Behrni taps koh-\npâ fapulzinati/ un eezels pahr fe-\nwim weenu Gatwu/ un zelfees\nuhs augſchu no tahs Semnes/\njo Jesreëta Deena buhs leela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Sakkajt us juhſeim Brahy-\nteem: Manni Laudis/ un uhs\njuhsahm Mahtahn: Al Ap-\nschehlota!\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Eita Sohdâ ar juhfo Mah-\nti/\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
